  "detailed_description": "Fantasy World Paradise<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOriginating from a fantasy future world amusement park, engage in battles with monsters within the park.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nConquest and Exploration<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn a semi open map, conquer giant monsters, claim rewards, and obtain rare equipment.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can also increase character strength by collecting monster cards and hidden items in the map.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeeling delighted when exploring new discoveries, and feeling a strong sense of achievement when conquering monsters.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSimple operation and refreshing sense of impact<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith simple operations, you can experience a good sense of impact",
